summary:
This is just a fish model I made and no longer need, feel free to use it for your mods.
(it doesn't have a texture)
descriptionHtml:
This was going to be a mounted fish trophy in a house mod I was going to make with a friend, which has since been scrapped.. So I am uploading the nif file here as a resource for anyone who wants to use it.
The fish has no textures on it.

Please credit me on the mod page if you do use it.

Sorry for the bad image by the way.
author: SkyrimForDaWin
